It's a fad of sorts....well maybe a permanent fad. OG paint, nice and faded 
and rusted up, lowered with rims, that sort of thing. Basically the older 
and more beat up looking the better.

Do a thesamba.com gallery search on "rat look" and you'll see tons of 
examples.

